<h2 id="a-deeper-dive-into-the-platforms-and-their-common-use-cases">A deeper dive into the platforms and their common use cases</h2>

<h3 id="nyckel">Nyckel</h3>

<p><a href="https://www.nyckel.com/custom-content-moderation-api">Nyckel</a>, a relative newcomer to the AI content moderation space, is gaining momentum among companies with large, dynamic online communities. Nyckel‚Äôs clients include entrepreneurial platform <a href="https://www.nyckel.com/blog/custom-spam-filter-gust-case-study/">Gust</a> and LGBTQ dating site <a href="https://www.nyckel.com/blog/content-moderation-of-social-network-taimi-case-study/">Taimi</a>.</p>

<p>Nyckel includes classification, search, detection, and OCR for image as well as text content. It also has deep learning options available to users with specific needs or problems that pre-trained models can‚Äôt address.</p>

<p>Nyckel offers several tiers of pricing, including a free option at 1,000 invokes per month.</p>

