<h3 id="sightengine">Sightengine</h3>

<p><a href="https://sightengine.com">Sightengine</a> specializes in visual content moderation solutions for NSFW and other offensive content.</p>

<p>Sightengine offers off-the-shelf models as well as a higher-tier, customized solution. Its APIs include image and video redaction, moderation, and anonymization as well as text moderation and embedded text detection. Sightengine‚Äôs main use cases are dating apps and sites, e-commerce, and content moderation.</p>

<p>Users looking to explore Sightengine can start with a free tier that allows for up to 2,000 invokes per month.</p>

