<h3 id="membrace">Membrace</h3>

<p><a href="https://membrace.ai/">Membrace</a> offers content moderation solutions with a focus on e-commerce, dating, and gaming sites.</p>

<p>Membrace‚Äôs solutions include 35 classes and 30 models, and the solution combines its machine learning (ML) with human-in-the-loop to moderate over 15 million cases per day. Membrace‚Äôs APIs detect problematic content across four types of data (video, image, text, and audio).</p>

<p>Membrace does not offer pricing details on their site, but they allow you to request a trial to test their platform.</p>

