<h3 id="microsoft-azure">Microsoft Azure</h3>

<p><a href="https://azure.microsoft.com/en-us/products/cognitive-services/content-moderator/">Azure‚Äôs Content Moderator</a> is one of over 200 products and services that the cloud platform currently offers.</p>

<p>The Content Moderator service offers Moderation APIs that scan and classify video, image, and text data. Users can either use Azure‚Äôs built-in list of offensive terms or add their own custom list to block any problematic text. Content Moderator‚Äôs concepts also include OCR to extract text from images.</p>

<p>Azure‚Äôs Content Moderator technically does not have a free program, but Microsoft offers up to 1,000 transactions for $1.00. It does not include human moderation in its services, but its human review tool allows users to implement their own human-in-the-loop.</p>

