<h3 id="webpurify">WebPurify</h3>

<p><a href="https://www.webpurify.com/">WebPurify</a> focuses on providing clean content to protect children and ensure that all users have a safe experience online. Their client base ranges from individual bloggers to Fortune 500 companies.</p>

<p>WebPurify offers live moderation services, automated AI, and a hybrid option as well. It allows for video, image, and text data inputs with very simple-to-implement APIs that use HTTP request formats. WebPurify also offers a 15-minute free video trial with no set-up or payment information required.</p>

